OL,3,CCouncillors cleared after 'badly-
OL,4,Cbehaved' SEND children comments
OL,6,FAn independent investigation into
OL,7,Fcontroversial comments made by three
OL,8,Fcouncillors about children with
OL,9,FSpecial Educational Needs and
OL,10,FDisabilities (SEND) during a debate,
OL,11,Fhas found they did not breach the
OL,12,Fcouncil's code of conduct.
OL,14,FThe comments on SEND provision in the
OL,15,Fcounty questioned whether some
OL,16,Fchildren "were just really badly
OL,17,Fbehaved", and "needed a form of strict
OL,18,Fcorrection".
