OL,3,CCouncillors cleared after 'badly-
OL,4,Cbehaved' SEND children comments
OL,6,FThe council received 281 complaints
OL,7,Freferencing all three councillors and
OL,8,Fthe comments that they made during the
OL,9,Fdebate on the SEND Analysis item at
OL,10,Fthe Children and Young People Overview
OL,11,Fand Scrutiny Committee, on Thursday 25
OL,12,FJanuary 2024.
OL,14,FCllr Jeff Morgan, Cllr Brian
OL,15,FHammersley and Cllr Clare Golby, all
OL,16,FConservatives, were criticised for the
OL,17,Flanguage they used in the meeting.
OL,19,FWhat were the comments made?
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
