OL,3,CCouncillors cleared after 'badly-
OL,4,Cbehaved' SEND children comments
OL,6,FCllr Morgan, the former cabinet member
OL,7,Ffor children and young people queried
OL,8,Fwhether some SEND children "were just
OL,9,Freally badly behaved" and "needed a
OL,10,Fform of strict correction."
OL,12,FCllr Hammersley asked: "Was there
OL,13,Fsomething in the water?" and "Where
OL,14,Fwere they all when I was at school?"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
