OL,3,CCouncillors cleared after 'badly-
OL,4,Cbehaved' SEND children comments
OL,6,FCllr Clare Golby questioned: "What
OL,7,Fcomes down to parenting and what comes
OL,8,Fdown to SEND issues ` how do we
OL,9,Fidentify that and what pathways do we
OL,10,Fput people on that perhaps don't have
OL,11,Fan SEND need but do have parenting
OL,12,Fskill shortages?"
OL,14,FAll three councillors apologised and
OL,15,Fwere removed from the Overview and
OL,16,FScrutiny Committee while a formal
OL,17,Finvestigation began.
OL,19,FKhizra Bano was one of the parents who
OL,20,Fchallenged the councillors' comments
OL,21,Fat the time.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
