OL,6,FWhen the three councillors made
OL,7,Fstatements, SEND Crisis Warwickshire,
OL,8,Fa parent carer group which represents
OL,9,Faround a thousand families in
OL,10,FWarwickshire, said while parents
OL,11,Fwelcomed them, they were not satisfied
OL,12,Fwith the apologies received.
OL,14,FThe leader of Warwickshire County
OL,15,FCouncil issued an apology and told ITV
OL,16,FNews Central that she was determined
OL,17,Fto "build the bridges" broken, after
OL,18,Fthe comments made.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
