OL,3,CCouncillors cleared after 'badly-
OL,4,Cbehaved' SEND children comments
OL,6,FAnd the Chief Executive of the Council
OL,7,Femphasised that the matter was being
OL,8,Ftaken extremely seriously, and that
OL,9,Ftime was now needed for an
OL,10,Finvestigation to be completed.
OL,12,FThe investigation, which was carried
OL,13,Fout by an external, independent
OL,14,Flawyer, found Cllr Morgan and Cllr
OL,15,FHammersley had failed to be respectful.
OL,17,FIt also found they failed to "champion
OL,18,Fthe needs of the whole community" and
OL,19,Fuphold the reputation of the council.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
