OL,3,CCouncillors cleared after 'badly-
OL,4,Cbehaved' SEND children comments
OL,6,FIt also found the councillors had been
OL,7,Fentitled to make the comments under
OL,8,Ffreedom of speech protections.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, Cllr Golby's words were not
OL,11,Fdeemed to have been disrespectful or
OL,12,F"caused reputational damage" or have
OL,13,Fevidenced a failure to champion the
OL,14,Fneeds of the whole community.
OL,16,FHow has Warwickshire County Council
OL,17,Fresponded?
