OL,6,FA spokesperson for Warwickshire County
OL,7,FCouncil said: "This has been a
OL,8,Fdifficult and lengthy process, and we
OL,9,Fwould like to thank everyone who
OL,10,Fcontributed to the investigation.
OL,12,F"We want to reassure residents that a
OL,13,Fthorough investigation has been
OL,14,Fundertaken and the views of all
OL,15,Fcomplainants were considered as part
OL,16,Fof that process.
